Both platforms, Aiki Wiki and Big Mother, address 100% of every problem in The Social Dilemma netflix documentary. This includes a piloted technology and a sophisticated business plan that can see considerable measurable effect within 18 months.

The entire DAO project is managed via the design principle of Aiki Wiki, which is win-win collaboration and participation. Our DAO is comprised of artists, designers, writers, scientists and thought influencers who are all taking on the "big tech" problem.
Taking on big tech with web3 solutions is the purpose of our DAO
